{"tid":125274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵淫狼扶手梯突襲 扭清潔阿嬸個頭強吻!!!!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2017-02-18T10:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-18T14:16:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46c8aa788baaef984db6eafda95a1d9db2303668","tid":125274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170217/large/1487335233_deef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170217%2Flarge%2F1487335233_deef.jpg&h=092cf6a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170218/56314583\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170218%2F56314583&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=5ccb0a51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170218%2F56314583&h=d0dcdab3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170218/56314583</a><br />\n江蘇蘇州市一處地鐵站日前發生一宗離奇非禮案，案中的受害人竟是一名50歲清潔大嬸。案發時，一名身材高大的男子緊緊尾隨該名大嬸，一起乘坐扶手電梯。當快到電梯頂時，男子突然捂住大嬸嘴巴，將她的頭扭向後強吻，之後逃去。事後，大嬸受到不少驚嚇。<br />\n據悉，案發時的片段從前晚開始到昨日不斷在蘇州人的朋友圈中流傳，據網傳，事發於本月15日上午10時許，在蘇州地鐵二號線陸慕站，一名男子跟着一名女清潔員上扶手電梯，突然撲向前，將該名年約50歲的女清潔員的頭扭向後，強吻對方。男子事後跳過閘機逃出地鐵站。<br />\n而女清潔員被突如其來的這一句嚇呆，事後報警。有指，她情緒還算穩定。至於疑犯據稱已落網，交由警方處理。<br />\n事發後，該地鐵站已將女清潔員，變成男性。代班的男清潔工稱，被強吻的女清潔員受到了不小的驚嚇，正在家休養，他不清楚今後是否會改成男清潔員。地鐵方面已將案件轉交警方處理。<br />\n微博<br />\n「千億莊家」肖建華神秘失蹤，《蘋果》精心炮製互動關係圖，讓大家能理清這名「大刁奇人」在各路權貴當中處於何種地位<br />\n【一圖睇晒】肖建華政商關係：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2krZskw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2krZskw&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=fb07f088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2krZskw</a>"},{"pid":"2a7c41618dcdd48addd87ae95b1f8f57b67519f6","tid":125274,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"少女我唔鋤愛呀婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ec173c788c96b3590ca3f703aaafdeeef95364","tid":125274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5fb3b3dcfb090861a88d3dada246c8b33557718","tid":125274,"uid":61030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd82e7b566ead7d7366d143bc0dd8c912efdab4","tid":125274,"uid":36660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a339697cfef420453232765bcec87f7c08676c1","tid":125274,"uid":58161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:30:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb693c75caa21a1f8d2189bef8fda419ac87238","tid":125274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:54:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d486c15acc0f136989a6f9be576e29c380526c2","tid":125274,"uid":52459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"阿姐好似無反抗，仲主動迎合<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}